{"tid":1750630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【區選光復香港】不分和勇多路齊攻 11.24和你投先取區會","createTime":"2019-11-24T12:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T12:56:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b713264a3586bb68f927fb48d61f08fd5f8a5c2","tid":1750630,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:52:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191124/60294298?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191124%2F60294298%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=4df47fdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191124%2F60294298%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=5ccf91d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191124/60294298?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1</a><br />\n<br />\n【區選光復香港】不分和勇多路齊攻 11.24和你投先取區會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5個月前，屬和屬勇是個值得爭論不休的話題。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【決戰區選】衝衝子籲投票彰民意：前線催淚彈都食 投票有咩難？<br />\n<br />\n5個月後的今天，說你是和，又會抗命上街抗爭；說我是勇，連儂牆又曾留下稜角分明的筆迹。<br />\n<br />\n和勇不分，皆因最高的山峯雖然只得一座，但登山的路從來不只一條。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【決戰區選】女拔教師爆眼心不盲 籲街頭議會全面開戰奪回政治權<br />\n<br />\n11.24，和勇多路齊攻，讓我們先取區會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191122/large/1574352910_6489.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191122%2Flarge%2F1574352910_6489.png&h=a01b8489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（設計圖片）<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【民陣國際人權日集會】<br />\n日期：12月8日<br />\n時間：下午2時至6時<br />\n地點：維園<br />\n主題：守護香港．和你同行<br />\n＊不反對通知書申請中<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n2019區選專頁<br />\n光復香港 11.24踢走共產黨<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【撐學生】<br />\n召集有心人 撐學生全年睇《蘋果》<br />\n立即按此<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n無懼警暴 學懂自救<br />\n《抗暴之戰●法例須知》讀果 上架 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【短片】【決戰區選】衝衝子籲投票彰民意：前線催淚彈都食 投票有咩難？<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【短片】【決戰區選】抗爭未完戰線不嫌多 珍惜手上一票（附民主派推薦名單）"},{"pid":"edecce0611e66fa0cb232807716e37aef17f93f6","tid":1750630,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投資，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ac706b579cde2a456b1851b0b11839818a48b83d","tid":1750630,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edecce0611e66fa0cb232807716e37aef17f93f6","tid":1750630,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投